descriptions.hotel_information:
EMB Hotel Memphis is a deluxe hotel located in the fashionable heart of Amsterdam. With its ivy- covered facade, this hotel is the perfect place to sample the charm of one of Europe's most cosmopolitan cities. 

Ideal for sight seeing, the Gresham Memphis is within walking distance from the famous Rijks Museum, Van Gough Museum and Heineken Brewery tour. 

Also the surrounding area is packed with boutiques, charming cafes and tempting bistros.

* Works will be carried out on the lobby,meeting rooms, hallways, rooms, restaurant and reception area.
01st November 2015 - 30th March 2016
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* St. Patrick’s Breakfast Room:
Informal and stylish breakfast room serving buffet and full English breakfasts, alongside speciality Dutch breads. 

* Memphis Bar:
Informal and stylish, modern bar with plump upholstered seating and sofas, offering hot and cold meals such as pasta, Memphis Burgers, dim sum and Dutch apple pie, alongside snacks, finger food and an array of alcoholic beverages. 

* Guests can start the day in the informal breakfast room, work out in the air-conditioned gym which offersg fruit, spring water and towels, relax with a drink and a snack in the bar, and have a coffee in the lobby with newspapers. 

* There are wireless Internet connections throughout the hotel, as well as a 24-hour business centre and two conference rooms.
descriptions.room_amenity: * With 74 guest rooms, the EMB Hotel Memphis is a welcoming hotel with personal service. Each room is equipped with in room entertainment system, telephone with voice mail, air conditioning, wireless internet, TV with pay options, radio, minibar, garment press and hairdryer.
descriptions.location_information: EMB Hotel Memphis is situated in fashionable Old South District, within walking distance to the heart of city and, World Trade Centre and close to RAI Exhibition Centre.The frequent tram outside the hotel takes under 10 minutes to reach the Dam Square and infamous red light district.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Distinctive charm and warmth, an ideal location in the fashionable heart of Amsterdam and excellent accommodation....

descriptions.hotel_information:
The Europa 92 Hotel is one of the few family hotels in Amsterdam. It is located in a more quiet area but still in the city center of Amsterdam. The hotel is near Leidseplein, Vondelpark, Rijksmuseum, Stedelijk Museum and Van Gogh Museum. 
It is a 3 star hotel providing basic and cozy accommodation with great services. Its location makes it ideal for business or travel visitors as it close to multiple points of interest, restaurants and bars, and shopping areas.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
Even though it is a small hotel it provides several facilities you can benefit from: 24 hour front desk, internet access, bar and lounge, coffee shop, TV in the lobby, luggage storage, laundry and dry cleaning, and fax/photocopying. 
The hotel personal speaks multiple languages therefore they are pleased to help you with everything they can. There is a terrace with garden on site for enjoying the sun while reading a book or having drinks. Europa 92 Hotel is a smoke-free hotel. Pets are allowed in this hotel. 
Tip: At the front desk of the hotel, you can purchase tickets for visiting all kinds of places. This way you won’t have to wait in line at the visiting centers. 

* Hotel\'s cosy bar is open every day until 1 am, and behind the hotel there’s a magnificent garden. If you spend time sitting here, the hustle and bustle of the city will seem very far away. It’s the perfect spot to relax after a day’s ramble through the glories of Amsterdam or simply to enjoy a drink. Also breakfast is served outside in the summer.

* Hotel Europa ’92 can also arrange to have your clothes washed, dry cleaned or ironed. If you get them  by 09.00,  they’re returned to you on the same day.

* Guests with laptops can make use of wireless Internet access throughout the hotel for a fee. The front desk is open round the clock and has a safe-deposit box for valuables.
descriptions.room_amenity:
Europa 92 Hotel has 47 spacious and bright rooms. In each room there is an over-the-bed artwork with pictures from major cities in the world like New York, London, Barcelona, Paris, and more. In the rooms there is internet access, free cribs/infant beds, cable TV, pay movies, private bathroom, hairdryer, iron and ironing board, and a safe. 
In 2012, 32 of the hotel’s rooms were renovated and they are all non-smoking ones. Check-in time starts after 1 PM and check-out time before 11 AM.

* The Hotel Europa 92, Amsterdam, features 47 guestrooms, all of which include telephones and televisions.
descriptions.location_information:
The hotel is placed in Oud-West district, 10 minutes’ walk from Leidse Square and Vondelpark, a must-see in Amsterdam. The Oud-West is a great area for people who are interested in musicals, theatres and parks. 
Amsterdam is said to be one of the world’s biggest “little” cities. This is a place where there is something for everybody; interesting places to visit, great shopping, and exciting nightlife. Near the hotel there is public transportation and stops are just 1 minute away from the hotel.

The hotel is accessible from anywhere in Amsterdam being positioned in the center of the city. If you are driving you should take Amsterdam Ring Road A10 to Museumsplein exit, and then follow directions to Vondelpark. 
The Eerste Constantijn Huygensstraat tram stop is a 1 minute walk away giving direct connection to the city centre, Amsterdam Central Station and the Lelylaan Station.
20 km from the hotel is Schiphol Airport from where you can take a train to the central rail station.

Amsterdam has a lot to offer to its visitors. Being checked in at Europa 92 Hotel gives you a greater opportunity to see more of the city. From the hotel, only minutes away there is Vondelpark, DeLamar Theater, Holland Casino, Melkweg, Diamond Amsterdam Museum, Museum Square, and Leidseplein.
Paulus Potterstrat is a well-known street for the three world-class museums that hosts: the Rijksmuseum, Het Stedelijk Museum, and the Van Gogh Museum.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Modern Amsterdam hotel close to Van Gogh Museum...

descriptions.hotel_information: The Nova Hotel is a friendly, 3-star hotel, located in 5 beautifully renovated historic buildings in the heart of Amsterdam. Famous shopping areas as well as many museums and the colourful flower markets are nearby. There are numerous excellent restaurants and cafes in the immediate vicinity. From Schiphol Airport the hotel can easily be reached by taxi or by direct train to Amsterdam Central Station. From Central Station you can either take a taxi (5 minutes) or the tram. The hotel is completely non-smoking!
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* The immediate neighbourhood is an eclectic mix of bars and restaurants, with numerous shopping streets, including Kalverstraat, and the Magna Plaza. 

* Famous throughout Europe for its decadent red-light district, a trip to Amsterdam would not be complete without a visit to this area, with its many bars, nightclubs and cabaret shows.
descriptions.room_amenity:
* The Nova Hotel Amsterdam consists of five authentic Amsterdam canal-side houses, combining a glorious past with modern conveniences. 

* The 61 hotel rooms behind the hotel's historic facade are furnished in warm colours and provided with every convenience. The hotel also has several three and four-persons rooms to make it easier to share a room with family and friends during your travels.
descriptions.location_information:
From the Nova Hotel, it's easy to set out on your discovery of Amsterdam by foot or tram since all the city's places of interest are within a short distance of the hotel. 

There are also numerous excellent restaurants and cafes in the immediate vicinity.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: We're located in 5 beautifully renovated historic buildings in the heart of Amsterdam..

descriptions.hotel_information: In an amazing location, just off Dam Square, right in the middle of Amsterdam's city center, you'll find Hotel Amsterdam De Roode Leeuw. This is where you want to stay if you're coming to Amsterdam.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* Restaurant De Roode Leeuw serves regional specialties and international dishes for lunch and dinner. There is also a terrace.

* The hotel facilities include a welcoming lobby with a 24-hour reception, a safe, the famous restaurant De Roode Leeuw, a newspaper stand, 2 conference rooms and a lift. In addition, guests are offere Internet access as well as room and laundry service and medical assistance.
descriptions.room_amenity: * All rooms feature broadband wired Internet access for notebooks, LCD flat-screen televisions with Internet access, digital movies and music CDs, coffee- and tea-making facilities, an electronic safe, and a minibar. The hotel is fully soundproofed and all rooms have individual climate control.
descriptions.location_information: Amsterdam De Roode Leeuw is located 50 meters off Dam Square, in the heart of Amsterdam.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Great central location, affordable rates, clean & comfortable rooms and friendly & attentive hospitality...

descriptions.hotel_information:
Built within three 19th century landhouses, this charming and elegant four-star boutique Bilderberg Jan Luyken Hotel combines design with classic elements of splendid Amsterdam architecture. 

This intimate four-star hotel consists of three historical Amsterdam mansions dating from the end of the 19th century. Once inside, you can see its classical design straightaway. But the rooms are thoroughly contemporary.

The guests rooms are filled with surprising and unexpected details. All of these rooms have a full range of modern amenities and comforts. Despite the hotel's classical exterior, the interior design is distinctly contemporary. The small scale and distinct personality of this boutique hotel make a stay there a memorable one.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* Breakfast room:
This breakfast room with stained-glass windows serves a buffet breakfast each morning. 

* Wines & Bites:
Drinks, afternoon coffee, appetizers, and light meals are served in this contemporary room with a patio garden and historic architectural details. The room is decorated in black and white, with red-and-chrome accents and plenty of upholstered chairs. Open from late morning until midnight. 

* Among the facilites you will find a bar, a small health centre equipped with a Jacuzzi, a steam bath and a solarium, a cosy reading lounge also featuring a satellite TV, massage facilites, Wi-Fi Internet connection in the whole building, a baby sitting service on request as well as a full time reception, staffed by a multilingual personnel. In short, you can find all the ingredients for a memorable stay in the amazing Amsterdam!
descriptions.room_amenity:
* This five-story hotel has 62 air-conditioned rooms spread out over three connected late-19th-century townhouses. Rooms have views of the quiet residential street. Wireless Internet access is available in all rooms.

* Historical architectural details such as bay windows or stained-glass windows blend with a striking contemporary decor: brown and burgundy fabrics, rich wooden furnishings, and glass-top tables. Special touches include soft comforters and hot water bottles. Other amenities include minibars, makeup mirrors, and electronic safes.
descriptions.location_information: Bilderberg Jan Luyken Hotel is a deluxe hotel quietly located in the cultural heart of Amsterdam, next to the Rijksmuseum and the Van Gogh Museum. The hotel is just a five minute walk to world-famous Leidseplein.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Combining design with classic elements of splendid Amsterdam architecture...

descriptions.hotel_information:
Bilderberg Garden Hotel is situated in the fashionable heart of Amsterdam, close to the centre of the old town. This renowned, small five star hotel combines international style and luxury with welcoming hospitality. 

You can experience this highly culinary character in every sense of the word. Whether during a business meeting in its recently renovated meeting rooms or during an individual get-a-way, you\'ll never forget the warm and intimate atmosphere.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* Mangerie de Kersentuin:

“The Cherry Orchard” restaurant is well-known by locals for its innovative, fresh Mediterranean-style cooking in a casual atmosphere with panoramic windows. Open weekdays for lunch and Monday-Saturday for dinner. 

* Bar de Kersepit:

Open onto the hotel lobby, this bar offers guests coffee, cocktails, or a selection of 100 whiskeys. Open daily from late morning through late night. 

* Hotel guest services include currency exchange, dry cleaning, 24-hour reception, and on-site parking lot. 

* There is wireless internet access throughout the hotel, and business services on request.
descriptions.room_amenity: * The hotel has 124 rooms on four floors with views over the leafy residential streets. All rooms have wireless Internet access, marble bathrooms bathrobes and slippers, and satellite TV with an in-house information channel.
descriptions.location_information: Bilderberg Garden Hotel is set in a quiet residential area between the RAI Congress Center and the museum district

descriptions.hotel_information: Inntel Hotels Amsterdam Centre is the best choice for your stays in Amsterdam thanks to its central location which is very close to the beautiful canals and historical heart of the Dutch capital.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* Start your day with a good breakfast in the hotel's sunny breakfast room offering a wide choice such as fresh fruit, a delightful boiled egg and several kinds of bread rolls. You can also have it served it in your room.

* The hotel's lounge-bar offers a pleasant way to end your day.

* The entire hotel offers wireless Internet services (WiFi). Also the hotel has 3 conference rooms with a maximum capacity of 8 people for your small meetings.
descriptions.room_amenity: * All 239 air conditioned rooms are furnished comfortably and are equipped with many facilities, such as luxurious bathrooms with hairdryer, coffee and tea facilities, Internet access, minibar and a safe.
descriptions.location_information: Inntel Hotels Amsterdam Centre  is situated in the historical heart of the city. Within walking distance you'll find many shopping streets and department stores.

descriptions.hotel_information: The Crowne Plaza Hotel Den Haag has been completely renovated in 2003 and offers a high standard of service and deluxe accommodation. Throughout the building one can admire numerous paintings from prominent Dutch artists, a unique ongoing exhibition owned by the hotel and included in the official "Guiness Book of Records."
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* The restaurant and the bar with its Grand Cafe make the hotel a culinary paradise. The private parking lot for 200 cars is unique in Hague. The Brasserie Promenade is a characteristic French cuisine à la carte restaurant. Each season our chef is inspired by what the season has to offer. It is open daily for lunch and dinner. Lunch is served between 12:00- 15:00, and dinner between 18:00 - 22:00. 

* The hotel's bar "The Couperus"  is open daily between 16:00 – 01:00. It exudes the atmosphere of a traditional English pub in which everyone soon feels at home.

* The hotel is the ultimate venue for meetings and conferences. 8 tasteful, fully-equipped conference and board rooms assures successful and comfortable meetings. 

* The hotel also cares about your health. You can engage in sports in the hotels fitness room or you can take advantage of the sauna situated in the hotel premises.
descriptions.room_amenity:
* All rooms are comfortable in design and come equipped with all modern conveniences, such as, a work area with computer, sitting area, coffee & tea facilities, laptop safe, bathrobes and slippers, an iron and ironing board to optimize work and/or relaxation. WIFI connection is available in all rooms. 

* All rooms have a balcony.
descriptions.location_information: Crowne Plaza Den Haag, which is surrounded by beautiful woodlands, is peacefully located in the direct vicinity of the Peace Palace, the O.P.C.W., the Yugoslavia Tribunal, the Netherlands Congress Centre, miniature city of Madurodam, Scheveningen beach with its sophisticated boulevard and the lively shopping centre of downtown The Hague.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: A high standard of service and deluxe accommodation...

descriptions.hotel_information: The ideal location for all that the city has to offer, and all possible on foot! Hotel's guests are mainly young and of varied nationality, it offers a pleasant informal atmosphere. The hotel looks out over the Rokin where the busy city life is warming up while you enjoy your breakfast in peace.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* At present there is no on-site restaurant at the Cordial Hotel, but there are numerous dining options within easy reach of the hotel. The hotel bar offers a selection of refreshments, alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks as well as a range of cocktails and is the perfect place to sit back and relax. Get a great start to your day with a delicious buffet style breakfast.

* During the summer, guests can enjoy their afternoon tea on the terrace, which overlooks the city. The daily newspaper can be found in the lobby. The Cordial Hotel’s comfortable atmosphere along with the attentive and friendly staff ensures that your stay will be an unforgettable one.
descriptions.room_amenity: * There are 50 rooms at the Cordial Hotel, each equipped with standard amenities to ensure a memorable stay. Room amenities include individually controlled air-conditioning and heating, color television with cable, direct dial telephone, work desk and an en-suite bathroom with bath/shower and hairdryer.
descriptions.location_information: The Cordial Hotel is a cozy two star hotel that is located in one of the most popular shopping areas of Amsterdam, between De Munt and the Dam. The canal touring boats and of course the canals themselves are on the doorstep. The hotel is close to the lively Zeedijk area, the Red Light District and the Central Station. This is the ideal location for visitors wishing to explore the city by foot.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Comfortable atmosphere along with the attentive and friendly staff...

descriptions.hotel_information:
The Mercure Amsterdam Amstel is a deluxe hotel strategically located 20 minutes away from the Schiphol International Airport, ideally situated on the outskirts of Amsterdam. All rooms in this modern hotel are attractively furnished. 

Comfortable facilities and convenience are qualities that the Mercure Amsterdam Amstel has to offer. High quality standards of service are what you can expect from the well-trained staff. The hotel is only minutes to fine dining, shopping and entertainment venues.
descriptions.hotel_amenity:
* Mercure Aan De Amstel Hotel also features restaurant \"L\'Ambiance\", the \"Coffee Corner\" and the typical Dutch \"Bruin Cafe\" with a wide range of drinks and meals. 

* For sport or relaxation, visit the Health Club with fitness room, squash court, sauna, solarium and Turkish bath.
descriptions.room_amenity: * Each of the 368 comfortably appointed guest rooms feature exceptional amenities such as air conditioning, data ports, wake up call, coffee/tea maker, mini bar and hair dryer. The rooms are all sound proofed with acoustics doors and double-glazing for your added convenience.
descriptions.location_information: The Mercure Amsterdam Amstel is a deluxe hotel strategically located 20 minutes away from the Schiphol International Airport, ideally situated on the outskirts of Amsterdam.
descriptions.hotel_introduction: Comfortable facilities and convenience are qualities that the Mercure Aan De Amstel has to offer...
